for property view if user click on property
you can use this URL
http://127.0.0.1:8000/getprops/propertydetail/?p_id=1
METHOD: GET
PARAMS: p_id

if property is not exist return 404 with this message
{
    "message": "property not found"
}

if user is not owner of property return 403 with this message
{
    "message": "you are not owner of this property"
}
